query:
UPDATE library_index SET
                mood_tags = $2,
                energy_level = $3,
                danceability = $4,
                valence = $5,
                song_type = $6,
                themes = $7,
                acousticness = $8,
                instrumentalness = $9,
                ai_analyzed = true,
                last_ai_analysis = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1
